divs: Sighting DetailsThere were exquisite big, bright lights but I couldnt describe the color, the ships color was an almost blackish muddy brown I was at my house and plating World of Warcraft And I notived a HUGE airbooming screech I first thought it was a test flight but it didnt look like a plane. It was sort of swirling around and the lightts were flashing off and on I kinda felt a bit sick in the stomach with a burning thing in my chest but after I lost sight all of the feelings went away making me feel drained wth no emotion. I lost sight of the object after I fell to my knees, writhing in agony.
